Single-sex schools are not a good idea, there are many aspects that can be defined as a positive side for being schools with both of male and female. For example, being in mixed schools might improve the students personality, because when the student faces different type of people, he/she will be aware of the different people, in addition, this kind of awareness would help the student to know how to deal in different situation what he/she might face while learning or outside the schools.
Furthermore, student in mixed school might has better vision in dealing with different gender because he/she will faces different experience while being in mixed school, this experiences will raise the student ability in knowing how to deal with the other gender, because communication with different gender can help the students to have an idea about the other gender.